data.description: Coming Soon!  Welcome to this beautifully renovated 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condominium, offering a modern and comfortable living space encompassing 700 square feet.    The kitchen boasts recent updates including stainless steel appliances, a stylish backsplash, and tile flooring, creating a contemporary and functional culinary space. This kitchen is perfect for both cooking enthusiasts and those who appreciate modern aesthetics.    Throughout the entire condominium, new Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring has been installed, providing a durable and attractive flooring solution that is easy to maintain.    The bathroom has also been updated with new tile, enhancing its overall look and functionality.    This condominium is ideally situated for urban living, with easy access to public transit, making commuting convenient for residents who rely on public transportation.    Furthermore, the property is conveniently located just 1/4 of a mile away from the vibrant Shops of Atlantic Station. This means you're only a short walk from an array of restaurants, shops, and entertainment options, providing a dynamic and diverse lifestyle right at your doorstep.    Additionally, for those in pursuit of higher education, the property is just 1 mile north of Georgia Tech, offering a convenient housing option for students, faculty, and anyone with ties to the university.    In summary, this renovated 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condominium offers modern and comfortable living with a range of updates. Its prime location, access to public transit, and proximity to the bustling amenities of Atlantic Station, along with its educational proximity to Georgia Tech, make it an excellent choice for those who value city living, convenience, and educational access.
